<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head> 
  <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" />
</head>
<body>  
  <%= render :partial=>'shared/mail_header' %><br /><br />
  Hi <%= @listing.seller_first_name %>,<br /><br />

  <span style="height:30px;">
    Good news! Someone has expressed interest in the pixi you posted.<br /><br />
    Click <%= link_to 'Check My Messages', conversations_url(status: 'received') %> to see the offer.
    If the pixi is no longer for sale, click <%= link_to 'Remove', get_url(@listing) %> to remove the pixi from the Board.</span><br /><br />
  
    To invoice for your pixi, you can:
    <ol type = "a">
      <li>Through the PixiChat&#0153; message center reply to the post, ask any questions or provide any instructions, and determine a meet-up spot, or<br /></li>
      <li>Click the blue Bill box on the toolbar in the application to send an invoice to the potential buyer. 
          Use the Comments section to provide additional instructions or details.<br /></li>
    </ol>
    There is a deal to be made. Go get it!
  </span><br /><br />

  <span>The Pixiboard Team</span><br /><br />   
  <%= render :partial=>'shared/mail_footer' %>
</body>
</html>

